{"tid":1755593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"星期日係絕好機會由民陣搞和理非百萬人大遊行","createTime":"2019-11-25T16:03:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T00:01:27.000Z","uid":45163,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"34832c69445f38ec9233173a48d7deb15900dce6","tid":1755593,"uid":45163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T16:03:49.000Z","msg":"自從勇武後 和理非出場機會少左好多<br />\n但係其實和理非遊行影響力先係最大，選舉後和理非士氣大振，今個星期絕對有可能號召到百萬人！<br />\n<br />\n首先 今次遊行必需和理非，不要勇武，因為咁樣和理非先敢出黎<br />\n<br />\n其次，由民陣搞，宣傳效果更佳<br />\n<br />\n最後，遊行終點站可能係poly ，順便救人。"},{"pid":"cd8faf92231d82352fea5c709d60b2daa2100e39","tid":1755593,"uid":234961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T16:04:34.000Z","msg":"求幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />P牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n推上熱門：新戰線&mdash;用建制方法贏建制<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1755527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1755527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9221e64b080c7a6954fc258447dfb7798b48d99e","tid":1755593,"uid":36808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T16:04:42.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻一阻大家時間<br />\n<br />\n希望手足可以幫下家長車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無言感激<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747239\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747239</a>"},{"pid":"27379649118d77f613914ae6509a881a06787aed","tid":1755593,"uid":261478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T16:06:09.000Z","msg":"雖然區選拎左389席<br />\n但咁嘅選舉制度下仲比建制狗拎到59席<br />\n只可以叫做小勝<br />\n大家開心完之後抗爭運動都要繼續落去<br />\nPOLY仲有一大班手足畀狗圍緊<br />\n仲有好多手足畀狗拉左畀人告緊<br />\n佢地等緊我地光復香港救佢地出黎<br />\n如果我地區選完就退<br />\n點對得住死左嘅手足<br />\n點對得住為我地擋子彈嘅手足<br />\n點對得住畀狗拉左嘅手足<br />\n所以18區要繼續開花<br />\n黎明行動要日日搞<br />\n組織全港大三罷<br />\n直到光復香港為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1754511/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1754511/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"15d6ba5066df7ae20508f8244bad225639a6fd90","tid":1755593,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T16:06:21.000Z","msg":"正視聽<br />\n和理非唔會因為有勇武人而唔出"},{"pid":"4d8830b1272fd98fdaf020a8137e696b089872a6","tid":1755593,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T16:31:25.000Z","msg":"啱<br />\n應該食著個勢搞和理非大遊行"},{"pid":"814e231e8169b95fb38118247afd215d2b9a2a14","tid":1755593,"uid":58803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T08:11:38.000Z","msg":"推啊！！！！<br />\n民陣搞遊行啦！！！！"},{"pid":"a92fdab0bab357f13a9988afef272cb93bd1a8b2","tid":1755593,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T08:13:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"164d1227a54405d28424cc968caf04f9474c3c91","tid":1755593,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T08:14:13.000Z","msg":"而家遊行仲有可能唔勇武?<br />\n就算和理非都畀班狗打到變勇武啦"},{"pid":"526b73eee6ac4184afd5fe98e2683945de68168d","tid":1755593,"uid":101906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T08:14:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5558ecd717764caa82d7873a4683f05df5b808cf","tid":1755593,"uid":29555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T08:14:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80f31676d34c1fc1f18967bd955e211c0a81ebe4","tid":1755593,"uid":313198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T08:16:46.000Z","msg":"你係咪坐左幾個月，不要勇武？仲想和平到?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6769c95dd7fa620c169775ff9d7b73d4cb7920a","tid":1755593,"uid":45163,"like":0,"disli